data.description: Stunning 20 acres with a pond overlooking two mesas west of the property. This is a stunning, peaceful property on blacktop road. 2 bedroom 1 bath home. Master bedroom has a large walk-in closet. Open living and dining area. The laundry room is off the back porch. The home is very clean and well maintained. The barn has hot & cold water, electricity, a tack room, feed room, and 4 stalls with runs currently assembled. The property also features a utility shed and loafing shed. Main barn is approximately 30 x 40 with addition approximately 26 x 40. Concrete pad to make a wash rack if needed.  Addition could house 4 additional stalls.
